Note on bank version
--------------------
The brief originally pinned v1.471; we shipped v2.0.3 because the author's
own repo only carries the current release. TSF (TinySoundFont) is agnostic
to GU version; the GM patches BellCurve routes through (19=Church Organ,
42=Cello, 48=String Ensemble, 66=Alto Sax, 89=Pad/Warm) are stable across
both versions.
